I'm updating my instructions above, but here are other changes.<br>
<br>
Borik will now apparently look at your Blacksmithing skill and let you know if you can do it yourself.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>You say, 'will you forge them for me' <br>
