Borik Darkanvil says 'A smith of your skill does not need my assistance in making the box, however I won't turn away your money.  Bring me three thousand platnium, the perilium, the brain, and the heart and I will make the box for you.'<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> <br>
